	<h1 class=3D"title">Checkouts Explained</h1>

	<div class=3D"entry">
		<div>Please note there is now right or wrong way when it comes to checkin=
g out as long as you get the final double but this guide will hopefully hel=
p beginners by showing them the most common ways to go as well as the safes=
t ways.</div>
<p>170&nbsp;=E2=80=93 The Big Daddy of all outshots T20, T20, DBull, Good l=
uck!<br>
167 -T20, T19, DBull the first two darts can be interchanged.</p>
<p>164 -There is actually two ways to take this out T20, T18, DB or T19, T1=
9, DBull, I like the second one because it seems easier to stay in a rhythm=
.</p>
<p>161- T20, T17, DBull again these first two darts ca be switched.<br>
160 =E2=80=93 This is the first three dart out that can get you to a regula=
r double, a good target number T20, T20, D40.</p>
<p>158 =E2=80=93 T20, T20, D19 not a very pretty out but it=E2=80=99s bette=
r than T18,T18, DBull!<br>
157- This is a classic T20, T19, D20 when ever you can shoot either of the =
first two darts first I usually will pick the higher of the two.</p>
<p>156 =E2=80=93 T20, T20, D18 the only way.<br>
155 =E2=80=93&nbsp;This one=E2=80=99s tough a good one to avoid&nbsp;T20, T=
19, D19.</p>
<p>154- T20, T18, D20,&nbsp;<em><strong>(Here=E2=80=99s a tip you can use i=
n many situations,<br>
Lets say you hit a single 20 with the first dart,<br>
from 134 you might as well go back at the triple 20.<br>
And lets say you hit a single 20 again, now you=E2=80=99re on 114 with one =
dart. Instead of going back to the triple 20, try the double bull it=E2=80=
=99s just as good as a triple 20, but a single bull gets you under 90 for y=
our next shot (89), a much higher percentage out than 94.)</strong><br>
</em></p>
<p>153 =E2=80=93 T20, T19, D18,&nbsp;This out has you all over the board tr=
y to avoid it.</p>
<p>152 =E2=80=93 Most people love this one T20, T20, D16.</p>
<p>151 =E2=80=93 T20, T17, D20 or T19, T18, D20 again I like the one that s=
tarts with the higher triple.</p>
<div class=3D"wordads-ad-wrapper wordads-ad-wrapper--inline"><div class=3D"=
wordads-ad"><div class=3D"wordads-ad-title">Advertisement</div><div class=
=3D"wordads-ad-content" id=3D"wordads-ad-931062" data-ad-height=3D"250" dat=
