he single leaves you on double bull, if you miss.</em></strong></p>
<p>122 =E2=80=93 T18, T18,D7, This double 7 may look strange but this the o=
nly way a pro would go on this one.</p>
<p>121 =E2=80=93 T20, T11, D14, or T17, T20, D5,<br>
