ut if you miss the first dart, but I prefer the one that starts with the hi=
gher triple.</p>
<p>120 =E2=80=93 T20, S20, D20 a good one for rhythm, all you need is a tri=
ple and a single 20 with the first two darts in either order.</p>
<p>119 =E2=80=93 T19, T12, D13</p>
